poldek test suite

BuildRequires: check-devel
Reqires: fakeroot

To run all tests:

$ make tests  # runs all tests made with check library
$ make sh-tests  # runs all tests written in shell (sh/ subdir)


sh/ test scripts may be executed separately:

$ ./sh/07-depsolver -h

Particular tests may be choosen:

$ ./sh/07-depsolver -v -t testSuggests
